beer.beer_description:
For our summer Limited Release we are dabbling with one of our favourite styles to drink and an absolute classic. OUROBOROS is a take on the legendary sours of old which we have added whole cherries and some vanilla to add a softness to the beer in its early stages.
This is the perfect summer sour to enjoy with friends (socially distanced of course) be careful though as this beer is pushing the imperial limit at 6% the alcohol is hidden with the use of fruit and vanilla. We have also siphoned off a few sneaky barrels which will be released in kegs after ageing it on more cherries and oak late 2020/2021.
